headline: Omnicom to Present at the J.P. Morgan Global Technology, Media and Communications Conference
summary: Omnicom (NYSE: OMC) today announced that it will present at the J.P. Morgan 53rd Annual Global Technology, Media and Communications Conference in Boston, Massachusetts on Wednesday, May 14, 2025 at 10:00 a.m. Eastern Time. Live and archived webcasts will be available at the investor relations section of www.omnicomgroup.com.
